title: Does Kamala Harris call on journalists who have exposed the organization of the nation?
subtitle: Two persons associated with the Medical Advancement Centre entered several meetings with the Family Planning Organization and the National Abortion Federation under the name of the fake Biomax company.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Kamala Harris refused to prosecute family planning for selling parts of the children who had had an abortion, but he sued journalists who had revealed that crime.
